Terrain Validation Rules:
1. Deserts, mountains and the sea, may only be selected on terrains on the edge of the map.
2. Sea Tiles and Lake Tiles may not be adjacent.  (if an tile is selected with an adjacent sea tile, do not show lake as an option, and vice versa.)
2. River tiles
  - may not run along the edges of Lakes, or the sea.
  - must have end points on one of the following: Sea, Lake, or the edge of the map. 


  
Setup Phase will have The following stages:
1. Terrain Setup
2. City District Setup
3. Street Setup
4. Guild Design 

Each of these stages should be shown in a Lifecycle diagram across the top of the page, in the Setup Phase Panel.
A "Done" button under each Stage name will allow the user to progress to the next stage. 
These done buttons should only be visible for the current stage. 